en listen to my appearance on local NPR station KERA to hear me talk about the history and stories in <strong>Entre\'e to Judaism. </strong>\r\n\r\n<a class="current" href="http://podcastdownload.npr.org/anon.npr-podcasts/podcast/77/510036/121221265/KERA_121221265.mp3?_kip_ipx=1078152060-1260833421" target="_self">http://podcastdownload.npr.org/anon.npr-podcasts/podcast/77/510036/121221265/KERA_121221265.mp3?_kip_ipx=1078152060-1260833421</a>\r\n\r\nDuring the next few weeks I will be speaking:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>November 24</strong>: Toledo JCC Book Presentation and Signing 7PM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>November 27</strong>: Jewish Museum of New York Informal Book Signing       10 AM</li>\r\n	<li><strong>December 5</strong>: Carlyn Galerie-Dallas-Book Signing and Cookie sampling    1-3 PM</li>\r\n	<li><strong>December 6</strong>: Temple Emanu-El-Dallas Hanukkah Presentation and Signing 9:30- 11:45 AM</li>\r\n	<li><strong>December 6</strong>: Private Book Signing Party</li>\r\n	<li><strong>December 9: </strong>Barnes and Noble Preston-Royal Book Signing 2-6 PM</li>\r\n	<li><strong>December 12</strong>: Neiman Marcus North Park- Book signing 2-5 PM</li>\r\n	<li><strong>December 16: </strong>TV appearance on Good Morning Texas KXTX</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nEat in Good Health!\r\n\r\nTina', 'Welcome to Tina\'s Kitchen', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '209-revision-10', '', '', '2009-12-14 16:55:25', '2009-12-14 23:55:25', '', 209, 'http://www.cookingandmore.com/4/209-revision-10', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
