INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (465, 2, '2010-11-19 10:30:49', '2010-11-19 17:30:49', '<p><img class="alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-439" title="CranberrySauce" src="http://www.cookingandmore.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/CranberrySauce-150x150.jpg" alt="CranberrySauce" width="150" height="150" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Dear Friends,</p>\r\n<p>Thanksgiving is almost here but don\'t get too excited about the turkey.  In a few days you will be thinking about potato latkes, Hanukkah gelt and candles on the menorah!</p>\r\n<p>Don\'t worry; I\'ve got you covered.  Look in my files for great Thanksgiving recipes; Turkey,Stuffing, Vegetarian Cornbread Dressing, Sweet Potato Cazuela to die for and an incredible apple, pear, and cranberry relish.</p>\r\n<p>For Hannukah try a great brisket or a sweet Moroccan couscous for a change.  And if you really want your Latkes to come out crispy, white and thick then check out my video for <strong><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9dzpLrKiAVw">How to Make Latkes</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p>Remember, if you are looking for a great Hannukah present that is truly "one size fits all", give <strong>Entree to Judaism </strong>and your gift will provide many hours of good reading and good eating!</p>\r\n<p>And last, but not least, check out my schedule below. I have been all over the country and in December I will even be in England at the Limmud conference so come and say hello and bring your cooking questions with you!</p>\r\n<p>Eat in Good Health!</p>\r\n<p>Tina</p>\r\n<p>The following is my November/December Schedule</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>November 4: Kansas City,MO</strong>Master Class and talk Women\'s Division of Federation </li>\r\n<li><strong>November 9: Dayton,OH</strong> Dayton JCC 7PM</li>\r\n<li><strong>November 10: Cincinnati,OH</strong>, Cincinnati JCC 7 PM</li>\r\n<li><strong>November 11: URJ Library NYC, </strong>Lunch and Learn for Staff 12-1</li>\r\n<li><strong>November 11: New York, NY, </strong>Manhattan JCC talk and demo 7-9</li>\r\n<li><strong>November 12: Cleveland, OH, </strong>Talk and Book Signing WRJ Central District Convention</li>\r\n<li><strong>November 12-14: Glencoe, IL,</strong> Scholar-in-Residence Am Shalom</li>\r\n<li><strong>November 28:  Dallas, TX</strong>, Book Signing Barnes and Noble, Preston Royal, 2-4</li>\r\n<li><strong>December 7: Dallas, TX</strong>, Talk, Temple Shalom, 7PM</li>\r\n<li><strong>December 12: Baltimore, Maryland,</strong> Women\'s League for Conservative Judaism Convention, talk and signing 10AM</li>\r\n<li><strong>December 24-30: Warwick, England</strong>, International LIMMUD conference, presenter, multiple classes</li>\r\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\r\n<p>If I\'m not coming to you then <a href="http://podcastdownload.npr.org/anon.npr-podcasts/podcast/77/510036/121221265/KERA_121221265.mp3?_kip_ipx=1078152060-1260833421" target="_blank">listen to my appearance on local NPR station KERA</a> to hear me talk about the history and stories in <strong>Entre\'e to Judaism.</strong></p>\r\n', 'Welcome to Tina\'s Kitchen', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '209-revision-41', '', '', '2010-11-19 10:30:49', '2010-11-19 17:30:49', '', 209, 'http://www.cookingandmore.com/209-revision-41/', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
